OKSIA OpenAI API Key

Place your OpenAI API key in one of these secure locations:

1. WordPress constant in wp-config.php:
   define('OKSIA_OPENAI_API_KEY', 'your-key-here');

2. Environment variable:
   OKSIA_OPENAI_API_KEY=your-key-here

3. Secure local file outside the plugin UI:
   wp-content/uploads/oksia-secret/openai-api-key.txt

This file is only an example and should not contain a live secret.
